    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184580/extras/3246217855ad81b545d7908449732285.poster.avif?t=1724784928\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184580/extras/3246217855ad81b545d7908449732285.webm?t=1724784928\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184580/extras/3246217855ad81b545d7908449732285.mp4?t=1724784928\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Elyme Arena</strong> is a multiplayer battleground where each player chooses their own special Element to battle against other players. Each Element, like Fire, Earth, Wind, or Water, has a unique playstyle, strengths, and weaknesses. They all are balanced enough for fair fights.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184580/extras/4b75d0ff3bd4151fadc815ccbc2e86c9.poster.avif?t=1724784928\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184580/extras/4b75d0ff3bd4151fadc815ccbc2e86c9.webm?t=1724784928\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184580/extras/4b75d0ff3bd4151fadc815ccbc2e86c9.mp4?t=1724784928\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Play Elyme Arena For Free! </strong><br>Invite your friends to compare your skills in each battle with each Element. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184580/extras/a099dbff7f93d12577215e08cdba0193.poster.avif?t=1724784928\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184580/extras/a099dbff7f93d12577215e08cdba0193.webm?t=1724784928\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184580/extras/a099dbff7f93d12577215e08cdba0193.mp4?t=1724784928\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Explore All Game Modes</strong><br>Elyme Arena offers a wide variety of battle styles, from Deathmatch to Tower Defense. <br>You can fight alone or in a team. Some fights require close co-op to achieve victory.<br><br><strong>Open New Elements</strong><br>As your skills develop, Elyme Arena opens for you new Elements to play with. <br>Get ready for many surprises with new unique Elements that will be revealed to you.",
